description: <p>Delius Unicase is a high quality comic \
  book lettering typeface with mixed uppercase and lowercase \
  letters for 'unicase' uses, such as in comic \
  strip lettering. It has a companion family, Delius.</p> \
  <p>Delius is based on the handwriting that the artist \
  Mar√≠a Delia Lozupone (whose pseudonym is Delius) uses \
  when she letters her own comic books. The same tool \
  that she uses to write (a big round marker) was used \
  to define Delius's stroke and ductus.</p>

